dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Edward Cox. May I have your name, please?
Thank you, Judith. Could you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight six two five seven and my date of birth is April eleventh, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Judith. I also need your current address to update our records. Can you provide that to me, please?
Of course, my current address is one two three Maple Street, Oakville, three four five six seven.
Thank you for the information, Judith. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Edward.
You're welcome, Judith. Thank you for your time. Have a great day!
